title: Nic McKinley
description:
In this episode Ellen sits down with ex C.I.A. officer and founder and CEO of Deliver Fund Nic McKinley. They discuss the dangers of social media, the need to hold our government accountable, and the courageous work Nic is doing along with Deliver Fund to fight human trafficking.
